OL,3,CMan tried to murder police officer
OL,4,Cafter throwing fire bomb outside
OL,5,Cstation
OL,7,FA man with a grudge against authority
OL,8,Fhas admitted attacking police officers
OL,9,Fas he ran amok outside a police
OL,10,Fstation armed with a Molotov cocktail,
OL,11,Fa knife, a hatchet and a wooden pole.
OL,13,FAlexander Dighton, 28, pleaded guilty
OL,14,Fat the Old Bailey on Friday to 10
OL,15,Fcharges relating to the incident at
OL,16,FTalbot Green police station in Rhondda
OL,17,FCynon Taf.
