OL,3,CMan tried to murder police officer
OL,4,Cafter throwing fire bomb outside
OL,5,Cstation
OL,7,FOn January 31, he was captured on CCTV
OL,8,Farriving across the street from the
OL,9,Fstation carrying a large rucksack and
OL,10,Fa long wooden pole.
OL,12,FShortly before 7pm, he lit a fire bomb
OL,13,Fand threw it at a police van.
OL,15,FWhen it failed to ignite, he poured
OL,16,Fthe contents of a second bottle on the
OL,17,Fvan bonnet and tried to set it alight.
