OL,3,CMan tried to murder police officer
OL,4,Cafter throwing fire bomb outside
OL,5,Cstation
OL,7,FHe went on to use the wooden pole to
OL,8,Fsmash the van windows. The pole
OL,9,Fsplintered before he turned his
OL,10,Fattention to target another police
OL,11,Fvehicle.
OL,13,FSouth Wales Police officers challenged
OL,14,Fhim outside the station after the
OL,15,Fdisturbance.
OL,17,FDighton, from Llantrisant, Rhondda
OL,18,FCynon Taf, ignored orders to drop his
OL,19,Fweapon and approached an officer
OL,20,Fsaying: "I'm fed up, I'm done."
