OL,3,CMan tried to murder police officer
OL,4,Cafter throwing fire bomb outside
OL,5,Cstation
OL,7,FThe defendant, who was wearing body
OL,8,Farmour, was tasered and sprayed to
OL,9,Flittle or no effect as he attacked
OL,10,Fpolice officers who tried to restrain
OL,11,Fhim.
OL,13,FHe swung the pole at one officer,
OL,14,Fpunched one in the head and stabbed
OL,15,Fanother in the leg.
OL,17,FTwo of the three injured officers were
OL,18,Ftaken to hospital for treatment.
OL,20,FOn being arrested, Dighton said: "I
OL,21,Fhave been damned from birth."
