OL,5,Cstation
OL,7,FHe admitted the attempted murder of
OL,8,FDetective Constable Jack Cotton,
OL,9,Fattempting to cause grievous bodily
OL,10,Fharm with intent to Sergeant Richard
OL,11,FColeman, assaulting Pc Joshua Emlyn
OL,12,Fand threatening Pc Stephanie Fleming
OL,13,Fwith an adapted wooden pole.
OL,15,FHe also pleaded guilty to the
OL,16,Fattempted arson of a police van, two
OL,17,Fcounts of damaging police property and
OL,18,Fhaving an adapted wooden pole, a knife
OL,19,Fand a hatchet.
