OL,7,FDetective Superintendent Andrew
OL,8,FWilliams, from Counter Terrorism
OL,9,FPolicing Wales, said this was "a stark
OL,10,Freminder of the dangers police
OL,11,Fofficers face every day."
OL,13,FHe continued: "I would like to thank
OL,14,Fthe South Wales Police officers who
OL,15,Fresponded to this incident for their
OL,16,Fswift and brave actions. They
OL,17,Fundoubtedly prevented further harm
OL,18,Fbeing caused to their colleagues due
OL,19,Fto their fast response and
OL,20,Fprofessionalism.
