OL,3,CMan tried to murder police officer
OL,4,Cafter throwing fire bomb outside
OL,5,Cstation
OL,7,F"The officers were fortunate to walk
OL,8,Faway without more serious injuries
OL,9,Fbeing inflicted. Dighton arrived at
OL,10,FTalbot Green Police station with the
OL,11,Fintent to cause serious harm to police
OL,12,Fofficers due to his anti-government
OL,13,Fmind-set. He saw the police as an
OL,14,Fextension of the government and he
OL,15,Fcame prepared to cause as much damage
OL,16,Fand destruction as he possibly could."
